    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The engine runs strong and the transmission shifts smoothly, ensuring a dependable driving experience for its next owner. While the exterior shows minor signs of regular use, such as small stone chips, the paint still holds a nice luster. The interior is clean and comfortable, with all electronic features and climate control working as intended. It\u2019s a solid, reliable choice for anyone needing a high-quality pre-owned vehicle.",
      "price": 34500.0,
